songs.title: Demo Outro
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Uhh, can you turn it down a little bit?
Not, not the headphones but the music a little bit?
I mean the music down a little bit, I mean down

I just came in here to say a couple words real quick, you know?
First I got to shoutout the engineer MD, for letting me use his shit, quality shit, forreal
I got to shoutout to my boy Al, you know, and Derek and everybody
I gotta shoutout the chick, this chick [?] and everybody
Everybody from East Lake to Eastdale
Southside to the Westside
North Chatt, East Chatt
Everybody that feel they gonna do something different so if you gonna do something different you might as well do it right
And I feel like that's what I was tryin' to do, so
Internet, that's all I really gotta say
Love yourselves
Be smart
Peace, soul, and happiness peeps
One, like that
